Anyway, there's this guy
from the 1 st Battalion, 2nd I nfantry,

24:51.740 --> 24:55.075
who swore that he could get him
naked photographs of the actor.

24:55.243 --> 24:57.953
I've been trying to tell him
that it's no-go, but he won't listen.

